column5: Found this video, couldn't believe it.  I have come across some aggressive Geese in my time, protecting young.  But not a rogue one like this.  This sucker had a pair, but lucky he came across this dog.  http://vitaminl.tv/video/1836
if I had it by the neck  it's goose would be cooked
Mine too... but answer you email Will ! lol
haha my dog would have murdered that goose
Mine too... but answer you email Will ! lol You still use email???
Yah.. if I didn't my goose would be cooked Dan !
i think that the third neck grab would have been the last if I was in his shoes.
I had one that hung around for a week.  It even let me pet it!  My kids, not so much... This pic was in my garage by the door inside the house!
